  <brief_title>Immediate Treatment vs Colposcopic Follow-up for Biopsy-Proven CIN 1</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Trial of Immediate Treatment vs. Colposcopic Follow-up for Biopsy-Proven CIN 1</official_title>
